Pseudo Code

Variables

int Servo int iMotor int iTurntimes int iSensorfood int iSensordispensed int iEmail int iFish

Function

Fish calculator = iTurntimes X iFish

Code

start

wait for set time

 if (Light sensor is blocked)

      turn motor depending on amount of fish in pond using function Fish Calculator

 else (Light sensors are not blocked)

      turn servo to dispense food and send email to use extra food has been used
Loop to beginning

Finish
